   Document Library:
   Proposed Restructuring of the Ninth Circuit
   This site contains background information and resources on
   congressional efforts to divide or restructure the Ninth Judicial
   Circuit. The official position of the Judicial Council of the Ninth
   Circuit is that the circuit is functioning well and its current
   structure should be maintained.

